{"tid":898067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp「度假模式」助打工仔隱身","createTime":"2018-11-11T12:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T12:30:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"07fcc7ba467b94c5b40e2c67ba499ee05e72291b","tid":898067,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:08:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181111/20543440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181111%2F20543440&d=iUfbqurwVDJIwkH6%2F7E%2FR8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=dd285c92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181111%2F20543440&h=9436290c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181111/20543440</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月11日 <br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp「度假模式」助打工仔隱身<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181111/large/wa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181111%2Flarge%2Fwa.jpg&h=84cd07da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有甚麼討厭得過放工還要不斷收到公司的追魂短訊呢？不就是讓老闆知道你「未讀」，甚至是「已讀不回」！有報道指即時通訊軟件WhatsApp（圖）終於知道用家的苦惱，將為打工仔提供收工後「隱身」的新功能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未定何時推出<br />\n<br />\n資訊科技網站WABetaInfo披露，WhatsApp正測試新版本，一個叫「度假」（Vacation）模式的新功能將會惠及廣大受薪一族，用家不一定要度假才能啟動此模式，只要下班後開啟，就可以在其他群組成員不知情下把對話「靜音」，不會被訊息騷擾之餘，也可以避免尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n現時在WhatsApp群組開啟「靜音」，雖然在收到訊息時不會彈出推送通知，但群組內及應用程式圖案上都會讓人知道你「未讀」又或已讀不回，隨時會不小心得罪老闆和同事。新版本可以免除這些心理壓力，用家只要放工後將討厭但又不能刪除的公司群組設為靜音，然後把群組「封存」，再開啟「度假」模式，收到新訊息後，已封存的群組不會自動出現在對話列表頂部，群組成員也不會知道你未讀，手機圖標上亦不會顯示你有未讀的短訊。<br />\n<br />\n不過，凡事有利亦有弊，使用此功能會容易錯過重要的公司訊息，用戶每每需手動到「封存」的群組查看，直至關閉度假模式，群組才會自動浮現在對話列表。暫時仍未清楚WhatsApp何時會正式推出「度假」模式。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n海洋原居民奇妙一刻　攝影冠軍關注填海「逼走牠們正確嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【飲食男女】冷面&mdash;藏不住&mdash;的熱腸（肥哥車仔麵）"},{"pid":"1a6058c2a531aea82f234b8c890f4037e2f69b6f","tid":898067,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:10:02.000Z","msg":"要俾老闆鬧點都走唔曳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1341bfc3efddc853789abba3a24923630013b617","tid":898067,"uid":65030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:25:35.000Z","msg":"咁咪仲衰，老細咪知你特登唔睇whatsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5d6d503773d8ba3590095a12a9508ea347c45b","tid":898067,"uid":77461,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"屌 我本身都冇朋友 轉埋隱身 死埋都冇人知<br />\n多謝whatsapp <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a70d066abf3fef1dded777451999b52d5429b66","tid":898067,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"轉頭咪打電話比你叫你睇whatsapp"},{"pid":"1c965a334f6fafc6cafa031dac5594e6e8fc45b5","tid":898067,"uid":40337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab5d6d503773d8ba3590095a12a9508ea347c45b","tid":898067,"uid":77461,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"屌 我本身都冇朋友 轉埋隱身 死埋都冇人知<br />\n多謝whatsapp <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:30:58.000Z","msg":"而家逼你用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}